Materials:
- Worsted weight (4) cotton yarn
- Size US H8 / 5.00 mm crochet hook
- Stitch markers - they help keep track of which round you are on
- Hairband

Pattern:
- Rd. 0: slip stitch onto the hairband
- Rd. 1: 1 sc, place stitch marker in first sc, 31 sc around {32 sts}
- Rd. 2: 2 sc in each st {64 sts}
- Rd. 3: 2 sc in each st {128 sts}
- Repeat until desired size!
